title: UST Syrup Pool
body:
# Stake CAKE tokens, to earn UST tokens!

Total Tokens: 150,000 UST
Distribution duration: 45 days
Start block: 4293992 (Jan 25th 4PM SGT)
Finish block: 5589992 (Mar 11th 4PM SGT)
Token rewards per block: 0.1157 UST

In order to host the UST Syrup Pool, we will need to provide a handful of mAsset farms, that will allow PancakeSwap users and the wider BSC economy to both stake and trade tokens representing Tesla, Amazon, Netflix and Google!

Farm 1 = mAMZN-UST @ 0.3x CAKE rewards
Farm 2 = mNFLX-UST @ 0.3x CAKE rewards
Farm 3 = mTSLA-UST @ 0.3x CAKE rewards
Farm 4 = mGOOGL-UST @ 0.3x CAKE rewards
Farm 5 = UST-BUSD @ 0.5x CAKE rewards

As usual, it needs to be approved via a vote.

Why do we need a vote? Since it dilutes rewards, the chefs want BSC's greatest community to make the decision themselves.
choices: Yes, we want UST and mAssets!
No, we don't want UST and mAssets!
author: 0x6eaf1b33b8672c5dc40aB8f4bA3A0111723126c7
